Done! I've created a complete Space Invaders game in a single HTML file: **space-invaders.html**

**Features:**
- **Canvas-based graphics** (800×600) with retro green-on-black aesthetic
- **Keyboard controls**: Arrow keys to move, spacebar to shoot
- **Scoring system**: Earn 10 × wave level points per enemy destroyed
- **Lives system**: Start with 3 lives, lose one when hit
- **Wave progression**: Automatically advances when all enemies cleared, increases difficulty
- **Gameplay**:
  - 20 enemies per wave that move side-to-side and descend
  - Enemies shoot randomly at the player
  - Collision detection for bullets and impacts
  - Game over when lives reach 0 or enemies reach the bottom
  - Restart button to play again

Just open the file in a web browser and start playing! The game gets progressively harder with each wave as enemy speed increases.
